<section id="faq" class="section-gap bg-white">
  <div class="container-shell">
    <p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p>
    <h2 class="h2 mt-5">Questions before you try it?</h2>
    <div class="mt-10 space-y-3">
      <details class="card group">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none font-heading text-lg font-bold">Which marketplaces are supported?</summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate">CarBasix is built to work with multiple international vehicle sources and marketplaces. Supported sources can expand over time.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="card group">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none font-heading text-lg font-bold">Is CarBasix only for importers?</summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate">No. It is primarily designed for importers and also useful for traders, resellers, brokers, and sourcing teams.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="card group">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none font-heading text-lg font-bold">Does it calculate total landed or import cost?</summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate">Yes. CarBasix helps estimate full landed cost, not just listing price, for better sourcing decisions.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="card group">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none font-heading text-lg font-bold">Can I open the original listing?</summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate">Yes. You can follow links back to the original source whenever you need deeper validation.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="card group">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none font-heading text-lg font-bold">Is there a free trial?</summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate">Yes. CarBasix offers a free trial so you can evaluate the workflow before committing.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="card group">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none font-heading text-lg font-bold">Do I need to install anything?</summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate">No. CarBasix is a web-based platform, so there is nothing to install.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="card group">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none font-heading text-lg font-bold">Can I save or mark listings for review later?</summary>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate">Yes. You can save, review, and prioritize listings so promising opportunities are easier to revisit.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
